    "body": "## Problem:\r\nNew autocmd event tests can miss coverage for handlers that change editor state while the event is firing.\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\nAdd a reusable functional test helper for disruptive autocmd handlers and exercise it with MarkSet and TextYankPost.\r\n\r\naddresses: #39609\r\n\r\nAI-assisted: Codex\r\n\r\n\r\ncc: @justinmk",
